This type of junction is OK for small networks of 5 or so short trains.

[[File:en/Community/Junctionary/3way basic3.png|none|frame|Simplest 3-way junction]]

===Pros===
*Cheap and easy to build
*Trains don't have to slow down to climb a slope

===Cons===
*Can only handle one train at a time
*Will cause traffic jams

